{
  "video_id": "X41iulkRqZU",
  "title": "12 truths I learned from life and writing | Anne Lamott",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12862.0,
      "end_time": 16340.0,
      "text": "My seven-year-old grandson sleeps just down the hall from me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16364.0,
      "end_time": 18300.0,
      "text": "and he wakes up a lot of mornings"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18540.0,
      "end_time": 19592.0,
      "text": "and he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19616.0,
      "end_time": 21830.0,
      "text": "\"You know, this could be the best day ever.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22385.0,
      "end_time": 24562.0,
      "text": "And other times, in the middle of the night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24586.0,
      "end_time": 27512.0,
      "text": "he calls out in a tremulous voice,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27536.0,
      "end_time": 30366.0,
      "text": "\"Nana, will you ever get sick and die?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31180.0,
      "end_time": 35460.0,
      "text": "I think this pretty much says it for me and most of the people I know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35484.0,
      "end_time": 38764.0,
      "text": "that we&#39;re a mixed grill of happy anticipation"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38788.0,
      "end_time": 40700.0,
      "text": "and dread."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40400.0,
      "end_time": 44622.0,
      "text": "So I sat down a few days before my 61st birthday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44646.0,
      "end_time": 49307.0,
      "text": "and I decided to compile a list of everything I know for sure."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49837.0,
      "end_time": 52960.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s so little truth in the popular culture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52984.0,
      "end_time": 55940.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s good to be sure of a few things."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 57370.0,
      "end_time": 59958.0,
      "text": "For instance, I am no longer 47,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 60665.0,
      "end_time": 63445.0,
      "text": "although this is the age I feel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 63469.0,
      "end_time": 66860.0,
      "text": "and the age I like to think of myself as being."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 66674.0,
      "end_time": 69347.0,
      "text": "My friend Paul used to say in his late 70s"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 69371.0,
      "end_time": 72954.0,
      "text": "that he felt like a young man with something really wrong with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 72978.0,
      "end_time": 76827.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 76852.0,
      "end_time": 79692.0,
      "text": "Our true person is outside of time and space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79716.0,
      "end_time": 81226.0,
      "text": "but looking at the paperwork,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81250.0,
      "end_time": 84585.0,
      "text": "I can, in fact, see that I was born in 1954."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 85173.0,
      "end_time": 88125.0,
      "text": "My inside self is outside of time and space."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88149.0,
      "end_time": 90194.0,
      "text": "It doesn&#39;t have an age."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 90218.0,
      "end_time": 93567.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m every age I&#39;ve ever been, and so are you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 93591.0,
      "end_time": 96274.0,
      "text": "although I can&#39;t help mentioning as an aside"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 96299.0,
      "end_time": 98930.0,
      "text": "that it might have been helpful if I hadn&#39;t followed"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98954.0,
      "end_time": 101475.0,
      "text": "the skin care rules of the &#39;60s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 101499.0,
      "end_time": 104893.0,
      "text": "which involved getting as much sun as possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 104917.0,
      "end_time": 107463.0,
      "text": "while slathered in baby oil"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 107487.0,
      "end_time": 111734.0,
      "text": "and basking in the glow of a tinfoil reflector shield."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 111758.0,
      "end_time": 113472.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113496.0,
      "end_time": 116940.0,
      "text": "It was so liberating, though, to face the truth"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116118.0,
      "end_time": 119466.0,
      "text": "that I was no longer in the last throes of middle age,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119490.0,
      "end_time": 123842.0,
      "text": "that I decided to write down every single true thing I know."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123866.0,
      "end_time": 127264.0,
      "text": "People feel really doomed and overwhelmed these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127288.0,
      "end_time": 130900.0,
      "text": "and they keep asking me what&#39;s true."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 130330.00000000001,
      "end_time": 136382.0,
      "text": "So I hope that my list of things I&#39;m almost positive about"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 136407.0,
      "end_time": 139472.0,
      "text": "might offer some basic operating instructions"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139496.0,
      "end_time": 143143.0,
      "text": "to anyone who is feeling really overwhelmed or beleaguered."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 143960.0,
      "end_time": 145842.0,
      "text": "Number one:"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145866.0,
      "end_time": 149527.0,
      "text": "the first and truest thing is that all truth is a paradox."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 149551.0,
      "end_time": 153866.0,
      "text": "Life is both a precious, unfathomably beautiful gift,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 153890.0,
      "end_time": 158571.0,
      "text": "and it&#39;s impossible here, on the incarnational side of things."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 158596.0,
      "end_time": 160216.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been a very bad match"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 160240.0,
      "end_time": 163506.0,
      "text": "for those of us who were born extremely sensitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 163530.0,
      "end_time": 166394.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so hard and weird that we sometimes wonder"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166418.0,
      "end_time": 167854.0,
      "text": "if we&#39;re being punked."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 168822.0,
      "end_time": 173776.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s filled simultaneously with heartbreaking sweetness and beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173800.0,
      "end_time": 175575.0,
      "text": "desperate poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175599.0,
      "end_time": 179143.0,
      "text": "floods and babies and acne and Mozart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 179167.0,
      "end_time": 181306.0,
      "text": "all swirled together."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 181330.0,
      "end_time": 183900.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think it&#39;s an ideal system."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 183924.0,
      "end_time": 187240.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 187264.0,
      "end_time": 190659.0,
      "text": "Number two: almost everything will work again"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 190683.0,
      "end_time": 193240.0,
      "text": "if you unplug it for a few minutes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 193480.0,
      "end_time": 195743.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195767.0,
      "end_time": 199490.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 199730.0,
      "end_time": 200796.0,
      "text": "including you."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 202795.0,
      "end_time": 206330.0,
      "text": "Three: there is almost nothing outside of you"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 206570.0,
      "end_time": 208969.0,
      "text": "that will help in any kind of lasting way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 208993.0,
      "end_time": 210957.0,
      "text": "unless you&#39;re waiting for an organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 211778.0,
      "end_time": 216715.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t buy, achieve or date serenity and peace of mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 216740.0,
      "end_time": 220514.0,
      "text": "This is the most horrible truth, and I so resent it."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 221369.0,
      "end_time": 223593.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s an inside job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223617.0,
      "end_time": 226435.0,
      "text": "and we can&#39;t arrange peace or lasting improvement"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 226459.0,
      "end_time": 228847.0,
      "text": "for the people we love most in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 228871.0,
      "end_time": 230951.0,
      "text": "They have to find their own ways,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230975.0,
      "end_time": 232597.0,
      "text": "their own answers."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 232621.0,
      "end_time": 236248.0,
      "text": "You can&#39;t run alongside your grown children"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 236272.0,
      "end_time": 240858.0,
      "text": "with sunscreen and ChapStick on their hero&#39;s journey."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240882.0,
      "end_time": 242999.0,
      "text": "You have to release them."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 243230.0,
      "end_time": 245418.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s disrespectful not to."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 246908.0,
      "end_time": 248767.0,
      "text": "And if it&#39;s someone else&#39;s problem,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 248791.0,
      "end_time": 251910.0,
      "text": "you probably don&#39;t have the answer, anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 251115.0,
      "end_time": 252307.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252331.0,
      "end_time": 255730.0,
      "text": "Our help is usually not very helpful."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255568.0,
      "end_time": 257993.0,
      "text": "Our help is often toxic."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 258644.0,
      "end_time": 261440.0,
      "text": "And help is the sunny side of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262656.0,
      "end_time": 265130.0,
      "text": "Stop helping so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265154.0,
      "end_time": 268611.0,
      "text": "Don&#39;t get your help and goodness all over everybody."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 268635.0,
      "end_time": 271147.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 271171.0,
      "end_time": 272832.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 272856.0,
      "end_time": 274829.0,
      "text": "This brings us to number four:"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 274853.0,
      "end_time": 278737.0,
      "text": "everyone is screwed up, broken, clingy and scared,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 278761.0,
      "end_time": 281736.0,
      "text": "even the people who seem to have it most together."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 281760.0,
      "end_time": 284199.0,
      "text": "They are much more like you than you would believe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 284223.0,
      "end_time": 288871.0,
      "text": "so try not to compare your insides to other people&#39;s outsides."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 288895.0,
      "end_time": 291760.0,
      "text": "It will only make you worse than you already are."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291785.0,
      "end_time": 294777.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 296920.0,
      "end_time": 299563.0,
      "text": "Also, you can&#39;t save, fix or rescue any of them"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 299587.0,
      "end_time": 301622.0,
      "text": "or get anyone sober."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 301646.0,
      "end_time": 304400.0,
      "text": "What helped me get clean and sober 30 years ago"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 304424.0,
      "end_time": 308340.0,
      "text": "was the catastrophe of my behavior and thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 308590.0,
      "end_time": 310650.0,
      "text": "So I asked some sober friends for help,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 310890.0,
      "end_time": 312230.0,
      "text": "and I turned to a higher power."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312470.0,
      "end_time": 316106.0,
      "text": "One acronym for God is the \"gift of desperation,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 316130.0,
      "end_time": 317558.0,
      "text": "G-O-D,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 317583.0,
      "end_time": 319615.0,
      "text": "or as a sober friend put it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 319639.0,
      "end_time": 324606.0,
      "text": "by the end I was deteriorating faster than I could lower my standards."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 324630.0,
      "end_time": 330941.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 330965.0,
      "end_time": 333275.0,
      "text": "So God might mean, in this case,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 333299.0,
      "end_time": 336440.0,
      "text": "\"me running out of any more good ideas.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 337352.0,
      "end_time": 341518.0,
      "text": "While fixing and saving and trying to rescue is futile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341542.0,
      "end_time": 344953.0,
      "text": "radical self-care is quantum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 344977.0,
      "end_time": 348592.0,
      "text": "and it radiates out from you into the atmosphere"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 348617.0,
      "end_time": 350262.0,
      "text": "like a little fresh air."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 350286.0,
      "end_time": 352867.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a huge gift to the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 352891.0,
      "end_time": 357401.0,
      "text": "When people respond by saying, \"Well, isn&#39;t she full of herself,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 357425.0,
      "end_time": 360391.0,
      "text": "just smile obliquely like Mona Lisa"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 360415.0,
      "end_time": 363377.0,
      "text": "and make both of you a nice cup of tea."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 364425.0,
      "end_time": 369108.0,
      "text": "Being full of affection for one&#39;s goofy, self-centered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 369132.0,
      "end_time": 371625.0,
      "text": "cranky, annoying self"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 371649.0,
      "end_time": 373178.0,
      "text": "is home."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 373202.0,
      "end_time": 375234.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s where world peace begins."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 376858.0,
      "end_time": 378575.0,
      "text": "Number five:"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 378599.0,
      "end_time": 383663.0,
      "text": "chocolate with 75 percent cacao is not actually a food."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 383687.0,
      "end_time": 387699.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 387723.0,
      "end_time": 391803.0,
      "text": "Its best use is as a bait in snake traps"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 391827.0,
      "end_time": 396387.0,
      "text": "or to balance the legs of wobbly chairs."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 396411.0,
      "end_time": 399662.0,
      "text": "It was never meant to be considered an edible."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 401685.0,
      "end_time": 403500.0,
      "text": "Number six --"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 403740.0,
      "end_time": 406578.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 406602.0,
      "end_time": 407857.0,
      "text": "writing."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 408694.0,
      "end_time": 413820.0,
      "text": "Every writer you know writes really terrible first drafts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 413106.0,
      "end_time": 415259.0,
      "text": "but they keep their butt in the chair."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 415283.0,
      "end_time": 417300.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the secret of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 417270.0,
      "end_time": 420227.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s probably the main difference between you and them."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 420251.0,
      "end_time": 421712.0,
      "text": "They just do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 421737.0,
      "end_time": 424303.0,
      "text": "They do it by prearrangement with themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 424327.0,
      "end_time": 426370.0,
      "text": "They do it as a debt of honor."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 427156.0,
      "end_time": 429450.0,
      "text": "They tell stories that come through them"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 429474.0,
      "end_time": 431984.0,
      "text": "one day at a time, little by little."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 432800.0,
      "end_time": 434234.0,
      "text": "When my older brother was in fourth grade,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 434258.0,
      "end_time": 438232.0,
      "text": "he had a term paper on birds due the next day,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 438256.0,
      "end_time": 440535.0,
      "text": "and he hadn&#39;t started."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 440560.0,
      "end_time": 444642.0,
      "text": "So my dad sat down with him with an Audubon book,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 444666.0,
      "end_time": 447100.0,
      "text": "paper, pencils and brads --"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 447340.0,
      "end_time": 452634.0,
      "text": "for those of you who have gotten a little less young and remember brads --"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 452658.0,
      "end_time": 455488.0,
      "text": "and he said to my brother,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 455512.0,
      "end_time": 458122.0,
      "text": "\"Just take it bird by bird, buddy."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 458146.0,
      "end_time": 460461.0,
      "text": "Just read about pelicans"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 460485.0,
      "end_time": 464341.0,
      "text": "and then write about pelicans in your own voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 464365.0,
      "end_time": 467520.0,
      "text": "And then find out about chickadees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 467544.0,
      "end_time": 470315.0,
      "text": "and tell us about them in your own voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 470339.0,
      "end_time": 472850.0,
      "text": "And then geese.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 472109.0,
      "end_time": 475857.0,
      "text": "So the two most important things about writing are: bird by bird"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 475881.0,
      "end_time": 478986.0,
      "text": "and really god-awful first drafts."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 479779.0,
      "end_time": 481454.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t know where to start,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 481478.0,
      "end_time": 484707.0,
      "text": "remember that every single thing that happened to you is yours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 484731.0,
      "end_time": 486247.0,
      "text": "and you get to tell it."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 486672.0,
      "end_time": 489834.0,
      "text": "If people wanted you to write more warmly about them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 489858.0,
      "end_time": 491578.0,
      "text": "they should&#39;ve behaved better."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 491602.0,
      "end_time": 494631.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 494656.0,
      "end_time": 497566.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 498965.0,
      "end_time": 501837.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re going to feel like hell if you wake up someday"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 501862.0,
      "end_time": 503623.0,
      "text": "and you never wrote the stuff"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 503647.0,
      "end_time": 507108.0,
      "text": "that is tugging on the sleeves of your heart:"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 507132.0,
      "end_time": 510528.0,
      "text": "your stories, memories, visions and songs --"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 510552.0,
      "end_time": 512205.0,
      "text": "your truth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 512229.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514540.00000000006,
      "text": "your version of things --"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 514780.0,
      "end_time": 515563.0,
      "text": "in your own voice."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 515587.0,
      "end_time": 518620.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s really all you have to offer us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 518860.0,
      "end_time": 520539.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s also why you were born."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 522308.0,
      "end_time": 526492.0,
      "text": "Seven: publication and temporary creative successes"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526517.0,
      "end_time": 528707.0,
      "text": "are something you have to recover from."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529564.0,
      "end_time": 532406.0,
      "text": "They kill as many people as not."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 532430.0,
      "end_time": 534959.0,
      "text": "They will hurt, damage and change you"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 534984.0,
      "end_time": 537980.0,
      "text": "in ways you cannot imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 537527.0,
      "end_time": 541430.0,
      "text": "The most degraded and evil people I&#39;ve ever known"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 541670.0,
      "end_time": 544176.0,
      "text": "are male writers who&#39;ve had huge best sellers."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 544913.0,
      "end_time": 549700.0,
      "text": "And yet, returning to number one, that all truth is paradox,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 549940.0,
      "end_time": 551519.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s also a miracle to get your work published,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 551543.0,
      "end_time": 554379.0,
      "text": "to get your stories read and heard."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 554403.0,
      "end_time": 557158.0,
      "text": "Just try to bust yourself gently of the fantasy"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 557182.0,
      "end_time": 559636.0,
      "text": "that publication will heal you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 559660.0,
      "end_time": 563743.0,
      "text": "that it will fill the Swiss-cheesy holes inside of you."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 563768.0,
      "end_time": 565362.0,
      "text": "It can&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 565386.0,
      "end_time": 566746.0,
      "text": "It won&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 566770.0,
      "end_time": 568475.0,
      "text": "But writing can."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 568499.0,
      "end_time": 572970.0,
      "text": "So can singing in a choir or a bluegrass band."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 572121.0,
      "end_time": 575428.0,
      "text": "So can painting community murals or birding"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 575452.0,
      "end_time": 578620.0,
      "text": "or fostering old dogs that no one else will."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 580390.0,
      "end_time": 583441.0,
      "text": "Number eight: families."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 584703.0,
      "end_time": 587799.0,
      "text": "Families are hard, hard, hard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 587823.0,
      "end_time": 591249.0,
      "text": "no matter how cherished and astonishing they may also be."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 591273.0,
      "end_time": 593399.0,
      "text": "Again, see number one."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 593423.0,
      "end_time": 594470.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 594494.0,
      "end_time": 598782.0,
      "text": "At family gatherings where you suddenly feel homicidal or suicidal --"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 598806.0,
      "end_time": 599822.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 599846.0,
      "end_time": 602177.0,
      "text": "remember that in all cases,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 602201.0,
      "end_time": 607665.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a miracle that any of us, specifically, were conceived and born."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 608340.0,
      "end_time": 610267.0,
      "text": "Earth is forgiveness school."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 610291.0,
      "end_time": 612401.0,
      "text": "It begins with forgiving yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 612425.0,
      "end_time": 615699.0,
      "text": "and then you might as well start at the dinner table."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 616460.0,
      "end_time": 620105.0,
      "text": "That way, you can do this work in comfortable pants."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 620129.0,
      "end_time": 623750.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 623990.0,
      "end_time": 625460.0,
      "text": "When William Blake said that we are here"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 625700.0,
      "end_time": 628580.0,
      "text": "to learn to endure the beams of love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 628820.0,
      "end_time": 631415.0,
      "text": "he knew that your family would be an intimate part of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 631439.0,
      "end_time": 635132.0,
      "text": "even as you want to run screaming for your cute little life."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 635631.0,
      "end_time": 638189.0,
      "text": "But I promise you are up to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 638214.0,
      "end_time": 641594.0,
      "text": "You can do it, Cinderella, you can do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 641618.0,
      "end_time": 643643.0,
      "text": "and you will be amazed."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 644984.0,
      "end_time": 646777.0,
      "text": "Nine: food."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 648700.0,
      "end_time": 650545.0,
      "text": "Try to do a little better."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 651317.0,
      "end_time": 653207.0,
      "text": "I think you know what I mean."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 653231.0,
      "end_time": 656876.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 662979.0,
      "end_time": 664130.0,
      "text": "Number 10 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 664154.0,
      "end_time": 666378.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 666402.0,
      "end_time": 667587.0,
      "text": "grace."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 668248.0,
      "end_time": 671355.0,
      "text": "Grace is spiritual WD-40,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 671379.0,
      "end_time": 672859.0,
      "text": "or water wings."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 672883.0,
      "end_time": 678850.0,
      "text": "The mystery of grace is that God loves Henry Kissinger and Vladimir Putin"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 678874.0,
      "end_time": 680330.0,
      "text": "and me"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 680570.0,
      "end_time": 684413.0,
      "text": "exactly as much as He or She loves your new grandchild."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 684808.0,
      "end_time": 686250.0,
      "text": "Go figure."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 686490.0,
      "end_time": 687826.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 687850.0,
      "end_time": 691187.0,
      "text": "The movement of grace is what changes us, heals us"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 691211.0,
      "end_time": 693209.0,
      "text": "and heals our world."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 693233.0,
      "end_time": 697300.0,
      "text": "To summon grace, say, \"Help,\" and then buckle up."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 697280.0,
      "end_time": 699718.0,
      "text": "Grace finds you exactly where you are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 699742.0,
      "end_time": 702266.0,
      "text": "but it doesn&#39;t leave you where it found you."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 702291.0,
      "end_time": 705387.0,
      "text": "And grace won&#39;t look like Casper the Friendly Ghost,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 705411.0,
      "end_time": 707160.0,
      "text": "regrettably."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 707400.0,
      "end_time": 709423.0,
      "text": "But the phone will ring or the mail will come"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 709447.0,
      "end_time": 710927.0,
      "text": "and then against all odds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 710951.0,
      "end_time": 713930.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll get your sense of humor about yourself back."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 714391.0,
      "end_time": 717709.0,
      "text": "Laughter really is carbonated holiness."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 718694.0,
      "end_time": 721386.0,
      "text": "It helps us breathe again and again"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 721410.0,
      "end_time": 723543.0,
      "text": "and gives us back to ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 723567.0,
      "end_time": 727304.0,
      "text": "and this gives us faith in life and each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 728315.0,
      "end_time": 732293.0,
      "text": "And remember -- grace always bats last."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 733472.0,
      "end_time": 736581.0,
      "text": "Eleven: God just means goodness."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 736605.0,
      "end_time": 739460.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s really not all that scary."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 739700.0,
      "end_time": 743520.0,
      "text": "It means the divine or a loving, animating intelligence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 743544.0,
      "end_time": 747269.0,
      "text": "or, as we learned from the great \"Deteriorata,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 747293.0,
      "end_time": 748901.0,
      "text": "\"the cosmic muffin.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 749620.0,
      "end_time": 752539.0,
      "text": "A good name for God is: \"Not me.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 753647.0,
      "end_time": 756393.0,
      "text": "Emerson said that the happiest person on Earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 756417.0,
      "end_time": 760595.0,
      "text": "is the one who learns from nature the lessons of worship."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 760619.0,
      "end_time": 763745.0,
      "text": "So go outside a lot and look up."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 763769.0,
      "end_time": 768272.0,
      "text": "My pastor said you can trap bees on the bottom of mason jars without lids"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 768296.0,
      "end_time": 770900.0,
      "text": "because they don&#39;t look up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 770330.0,
      "end_time": 774433.0,
      "text": "so they just walk around bitterly bumping into the glass walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 774457.0,
      "end_time": 776825.0,
      "text": "Go outside. Look up."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 776849.0,
      "end_time": 778216.0,
      "text": "Secret of life."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 779297.0,
      "end_time": 781161.0,
      "text": "And finally: death."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 782193.0,
      "end_time": 783473.0,
      "text": "Number 12."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 784466.0,
      "end_time": 786243.0,
      "text": "Wow and yikes."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 787195.0,
      "end_time": 791420.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so hard to bear when the few people you cannot live without die."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 791444.0,
      "end_time": 795800.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ll never get over these losses, and no matter what the culture says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 795105.0,
      "end_time": 796972.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not supposed to."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 796996.0,
      "end_time": 802139.0,
      "text": "We Christians like to think of death as a major change of address,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 802163.0,
      "end_time": 806749.0,
      "text": "but in any case, the person will live again fully in your heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 806773.0,
      "end_time": 808765.0,
      "text": "if you don&#39;t seal it off."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 808789.0,
      "end_time": 811557.0,
      "text": "Like Leonard Cohen said, \"There are cracks in everything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 811581.0,
      "end_time": 813434.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s how the light gets in.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 813458.0,
      "end_time": 817360.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s how we feel our people again fully alive."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 819600.0,
      "end_time": 823700.0,
      "text": "Also, the people will make you laugh out loud"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 823950.0,
      "end_time": 826161.0,
      "text": "at the most inconvenient times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 826185.0,
      "end_time": 828258.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s the great good news."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 828283.0,
      "end_time": 832738.0,
      "text": "But their absence will also be a lifelong nightmare of homesickness for you."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 832762.0,
      "end_time": 837443.0,
      "text": "Grief and friends, time and tears will heal you to some extent."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 837467.0,
      "end_time": 841718.0,
      "text": "Tears will bathe and baptize and hydrate and moisturize you"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 841742.0,
      "end_time": 844700.0,
      "text": "and the ground on which you walk."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 844950.0,
      "end_time": 847126.0,
      "text": "Do you know the first thing that God says to Moses?"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 847848.0,
      "end_time": 850342.0,
      "text": "He says, \"Take off your shoes.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 850899.0,
      "end_time": 854939.0,
      "text": "Because this is holy ground, all evidence to the contrary."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 854963.0,
      "end_time": 858280.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s hard to believe, but it&#39;s the truest thing I know."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 858520.0,
      "end_time": 862194.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re a little bit older, like my tiny personal self,"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 862218.0,
      "end_time": 866240.0,
      "text": "you realize that death is as sacred as birth."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 866605.0,
      "end_time": 869599.0,
      "text": "And don&#39;t worry -- get on with your life."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 870225.0,
      "end_time": 874720.0,
      "text": "Almost every single death is easy and gentle"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 874744.0,
      "end_time": 877760.0,
      "text": "with the very best people surrounding you"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 877784.0,
      "end_time": 879627.0,
      "text": "for as long as you need."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 879651.0,
      "end_time": 881290.0,
      "text": "You won&#39;t be alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 882506.0,
      "end_time": 886174.0,
      "text": "They&#39;ll help you cross over to whatever awaits us."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 886691.0,
      "end_time": 888428.0,
      "text": "As Ram Dass said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 888452.0,
      "end_time": 890312.0,
      "text": "\"When all is said and done,"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 890336.0,
      "end_time": 893336.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re really just all walking each other home.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 894844.0,
      "end_time": 896432.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 896456.0,
      "end_time": 898558.0,
      "text": "but if I think of anything else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 898582.0,
      "end_time": 900440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll let you know."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 900680.0,
      "end_time": 901271.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 901295.0,
      "end_time": 902873.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 902898.0,
      "end_time": 904174.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 904198.0,
      "end_time": 906600.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 906300.0,
      "end_time": 908184.0,
      "text": "I was very surprised to be asked to come,"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 908208.0,
      "end_time": 910891.0,
      "text": "because it is not my realm,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 910915.0,
      "end_time": 913242.0,
      "text": "technology or design or entertainment."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 913266.0,
      "end_time": 916447.0,
      "text": "I mean, my realm is sort of faith and writing"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 916471.0,
      "end_time": 919421.0,
      "text": "and kind of lurching along together."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 919445.0,
      "end_time": 921208.0,
      "text": "And I was surprised,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 921232.0,
      "end_time": 925505.0,
      "text": "but they said I could give a talk, and I said I&#39;d love to."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 925529.0,
      "end_time": 927581.0,
      "text": "(Video) If you don&#39;t know where to start,"
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 927605.0,
      "end_time": 930730.0,
      "text": "remember that every single thing that happened to you is yours"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 930754.0,
      "end_time": 932132.0,
      "text": "and you get to tell it."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 932156.0,
      "end_time": 935261.0,
      "text": "Anne Lamott: People are very frightened and feel really doomed"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 935285.0,
      "end_time": 936473.0,
      "text": "in America these days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 936497.0,
      "end_time": 939637.0,
      "text": "and I just wanted to help people get their sense of humor about it"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 939662.0,
      "end_time": 943260.0,
      "text": "and to realize how much isn&#39;t a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 943284.0,
      "end_time": 946510.0,
      "text": "If you take an action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 947359.0,
      "end_time": 950922.0,
      "text": "take a really healthy or loving or friendly action,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 950946.0,
      "end_time": 953807.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll have loving and friendly feelings."
    }
  ]
}